        <p>Liver cancer surgery main types: primary liver cancer (HCC) మరియు metastatic liver disease (most commonly from colorectal cancer).</p>
        <p>HCC కి, liver function (Child-Pugh score) మరియు tumour characteristics surgery candidacy determine చేస్తాయి. Barcelona Clinic Liver Cancer (BCLC) staging surgery indication guide చేస్తుంది. Adequate future liver remnant (FLR) surgery safety కి critical.</p>
